thread.title: BRIEF-Hainan Haide Industry sees FY 2017 net profit up about 2082.9 pct to 2519.5 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Hainan Haide Industry sees FY 2017 net profit up about 2082.9 pct to 2519.5 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - hainan haide industry co ltd

text:
Jan 25(Reuters) - Hainan Haide Industry Co Ltd
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by about 2082.9 percent to 2519.5 percent, or to be about 65 million yuan to 78 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 3 million yuan
* Says increased income from bad asset management business is the main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/VruX8X
